info.description: # preshed: Cython Hash Table for Pre-Hashed Keys Simple but high performance Cython hash table mapping pre-randomized keys to `void*` values. Inspired by [Jeff Preshing](http://preshing.com/20130107/this-hash-table-is-faster-than-a-judy-array/).
